NAME:
	Filter Elevation Scan Reflectivity Product

DESCRIPTION:
	The segmtalg with filter on produces an intermediate product 
	which contains following data:
	/* Define the structure of the radial message. */
	typedef struct {

   	Base_data_header bdh;
   	unsigned char    radar_data[RADAR_DATA_SIZE];

	} Compact_radial;

	/* Define the structure of the elevation product. */
	typedef struct {

   	int num_radials;
   	short type;
   	short elev_ind;
   	Compact_radial radial[MAX_RADIALS_ELEV];

	} Compact_basedata_elev;
	
	The linear buffer size is about 1 MB 

